  "3058360": {
    "name": "法国小馆儿模拟器",
    "steam_appid": 3058360,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058360/extras/18b2d67f7a543a3c3dcd6b2f0d34bdef.avif?t=1772166041\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【游戏支持1-4人联机模式】【雇员系统已实装，一个人也能爽玩】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好开启一段充满奇趣的欢乐旅程了吗？ 在世界上游客最多的巴黎心脏地带，亲自经营一家法式风情餐馆儿。沉浸在真实的巴黎城市氛围中，欣赏奥斯曼风格的建筑和埃菲尔铁塔的美景，尽享法式美食的魅力。通过设计应季菜单，优化人力配置和提升食客满意度等方面，让您的法式小馆蜕变为塞纳河畔的餐饮传奇！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058360/extras/744431b805a2db21ec3eab3a0f9edf7f.avif?t=1772166041\" width=616 height=72 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为巴黎繁华林荫大道上一家小餐馆的老板，您即将迎来盛大的开业日。精心布置店面，摆放桌椅，订购首批优质食材，并设计一份吸引食客的精美菜单。准备就绪后，正式开门迎客，迎接您的第一批顾客，开启餐饮之旅！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058360/extras/c1dafe37ff1f01290ed0a2f18e056d9a.poster.avif?t=1772166041\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058360/extras/c1dafe37ff1f01290ed0a2f18e056d9a.webm?t=1772166041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058360/extras/c1dafe37ff1f01290ed0a2f18e056d9a.mp4?t=1772166041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058360/extras/a5c29390644740e28f9e180e5fac2963.avif?t=1772166041\" width=616 height=72 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦开业，高效运营尤为关键。精心组织团队，合理分工，确保每位顾客都能得到及时、礼貌的服务。及时将顾客安排在合适的用餐区，高效管理订单，确保每位顾客离开餐厅时都确保顾客满意而归！让小费不断增长，营业额飙升，赚得停不下来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058360/extras/c07e686792a4d252df7c49726f26fe0b.poster.avif?t=1772166041\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058360/extras/c07e686792a4d252df7c49726f26fe0b.webm?t=1772166041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058360/extras/c07e686792a4d252df7c49726f26fe0b.mp4?t=1772166041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058360/extras/08f6d0f3352ee1fb71672977efa04bc7.avif?t=1772166041\" width=616 height=72 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吧台管理是餐厅经营的重要环节。始终提供优质葡萄酒、咖啡、啤酒和非酒精饮料。在向顾客提供饮料和咖啡时需举止优雅，确保顾客满意。管理好饮品供应，防止短缺，确保您的吧台始终备货充足，满足顾客多样化需求，吸引顾客持续光临。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058360/extras/f51d98220f36cc9d26d9d7097ad11645.poster.avif?t=1772166041\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058360/extras/f51d98220f36cc9d26d9d7097ad11645.webm?t=1772166041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058360/extras/f51d98220f36cc9d26d9d7097ad11645.mp4?t=1772166041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058360/extras/64cd1fc001491e91abf4ae768aa1b79a.avif?t=1772166041\" width=616 height=72 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有效管理商品和利润空间对餐厅盈利至关重要。密切监控原材料供应，避免浪费，与供应商谈判协商以获得最优价格。使用管理工具分析成本、调整价格，在为顾客提供优质产品的同时实现利润最大化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058360/extras/f36ebb70edee72d10a6aee8db8e62237.poster.avif?t=1772166041\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058360/extras/f36ebb70edee72d10a6aee8db8e62237.webm?t=1772166041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058360/extras/f36ebb70edee72d10a6aee8db8e62237.mp4?t=1772166041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058360/extras/d58b20287eb1054777e78df134ba9ed6.avif?t=1772166041\" width=616 height=72 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当您征服顾客满意度、盈利能力与服务品质三大关键指标，每场胜利都将解锁闪耀里程碑——菜单焕发法式创意之光，新菜式持续拓展味觉疆域，让巴黎人为您的餐饮帝国欢呼！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
